summaries.summary: Contrary to popular belief, lorem ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical latin literature from 45 bc, making it over 2000 years old. Richard mcclintock, a latin professor at hampden-sydney college in virginia, looked up one of the more obscure latin words, consectetur, from a lorem ipsum passage.

You can refer external content from other documents from your documentation or from external public or private repositories. The external content can either added using liquid sintax or custom liquid tags. There is no limit about how many external public repositories you refer the number of the external private repositories depends on the private access key type you configure.
